Sir Thomas Jernegan於1380年出生在英國諾福爾可格亞特 亞爾姆斯時，他的父親John Shelton Jernegan III16歲，母親Margaret Vis de Lou36歲。他於1409年與Joan Appleyard在英國英格蘭素福爾可索莫利頓結婚。他們至少是1個兒子的父母。他去世於1450年在威爾士凱爾納方史爾享年70歲，埋葬在英國素福爾可索莫利頓。"},"zh-hans":{"1380–1450":"1380年–1450年","1393–1450":"1393年–1450年","1410–1474":"1410年–1474年","1364–1401":"1364年–1401年","1345–1388":"1345年–1388年","1401":"1401年","1345":"1345年","1388":"1388年","1410":"1410年","1364":"1364年","1474":"1474年","1374":"1374年","1450":"1450年","1409":"1409年","1382":"1382年","1393":"1393年","1380":"1380年","Conwy, Caernarfonshire, Wales":"威尔士凱爾納方史爾康維","Somerleyton, Suffolk, England":"英国素福爾可索莫利頓","Waveney, Suffolk, England":"英国素福爾可瓦文利","Somerleyton, Suffolk, England, United Kingdom":"英国素福爾可索莫利頓","Caernarfonshire, Wales":"威尔士凱爾納方史爾","England, United Kingdom":"英国英格兰","Great Yarmouth, Norfolk, England":"英国諾福爾可格亞特 亞爾姆斯","lifeSummary":"当Sir Thomas Jernegan于1380年出生在英国諾福爾可格亞特 亞爾姆斯时，他的父亲John Shelton Jernegan III16岁，母亲Margaret Vis de Lou36岁。他于1409年与Joan Appleyard在英国英格兰素福爾可索莫利頓结婚。他们至少是1个儿子的父母。他去世于1450年在威尔士凱爾納方史爾享年70岁，埋葬在英国素福爾可索莫利頓。"},"hr":{"1380–1450":"1380.–1450.","1393–1450":"1393–1450.","1410–1474":"1410.–1474","1364–1401":"1364–1401.","1345–1388":"1345–1388.","1401":"1401.","1345":"1345","1388":"1388.","1410":"1410.","1364":"1364","1474":"1474","1374":"1374.","1450":"1450.","1409":"1409.","1382":"1382","1393":"1393","1380":"1380.","Conwy, Caernarfonshire, Wales":"Conwy, Caernarfonshire, Wales","Somerleyton, Suffolk, England":"Somerleyton, Suffolk, England","Waveney, Suffolk, England":"Waveney, Suffolk, England","Somerleyton, Suffolk, England, United Kingdom":"Somerleyton, Suffolk, England","Caernarfonshire, Wales":"Caernarfonshire, Wales","England, United Kingdom":"Engleska, United Kingdom","Great Yarmouth, Norfolk, England":"Great Yarmouth, Norfolk, England"},"cs":{"1380–1450":"1380–1450","1393–1450":"1393–1450","1410–1474":"1410–1474","1364–1401":"1364–1401","1345–1388":"1345–1388","1401":"1401","1345":"1345","1388":"1388","1410":"1410","1364":"1364","1474":"1474","